featured_reviews.review_id: Situated in the centre of Munnar. Easily visible as it is situated on top of one small mountain. Very well maintained and big enough to hold followers. A well cleaned washroom is also there. The view from the Masjid is really awesome. Most of the visitors will be tourists only here.

featured_reviews.review_id: Beautiful masjid, can be seen from a distance due to its high elevation. Calm and quiet place. There is a ladies prayer area in the beginning. Attractive architecture in and out. After all it's very useful for travellers. May Allah reward everyone who contributed in building and maintaining this masjid.

featured_reviews.review_id: Munnar Juma masjid is located on a small hill and very near to munnar main town. It's a best and beautiful place for praying. Always busy with tourists and pilgrims. Parking facility available. While going from the main town we can see the beauty of masjid. It has so many good views.
